work.summary:
I was part of Alright's PTD (Publisher Trending Desk) team where I worked as an analyst and developer researching technologies so that we could help partner content producers to have better income.

In addition to the news portals developed using Wordpress technology, I was also part of several researches and developments within the company.

Main activities carried out:

• Research and development of algorithms aimed at optimizing websites for programmatic media;
• Development and maintenance of internal systems to improve and control the company's processes;
• Maintenance and optimization of partner sites to obtain better results;
• Development of news portals for partners;
• Development of api's for integration of news portals with mobile applications;
• Creation and maintenance of servers for testing, development and production environments
